@startuml Customer_Booking_Flow  
  
title Customer Journey - Choose Movie & Buy Ticket  
  
actor "Customer" as C  
participant "Frontend SPA" as FE  
participant "API Gateway" as GW  
participant "Movie Service" as MS  
participant "Booking Service" as BS  
participant "Payment Service" as PS  
participant "User Service" as US  
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ  
  
== Step 1: Browse Movies ==  
  
C -> FE : Browse /movies  
FE -> GW : GET /api/movies  
GW -> MS : GET /api/movies  
MS --> GW : Movie list (JSON)  
GW --> FE : Movie list  
FE --> C : Display movie cards  
  
== Step 2: View Movie Details & Showtimes ==  
  
C -> FE : Click movie -> /movies/:id  
FE -> GW : GET /api/movies/:id  
FE -> GW : GET /api/showtimes?movie_id=X  
FE -> GW : GET /api/rooms  
GW -> MS : Forward all 3 requests  
MS --> GW : Movie + Showtimes + Rooms  
GW --> FE : Combined data  
FE --> C : Show calendar with showtimes\n(date, time, room, price)  
  
== Step 3: Select Seats ==  
  
C -> FE : Pick showtime -> /book/:showtimeId  
FE -> GW : GET /api/showtimes/:id/seats  
GW -> BS : GET /api/showtimes/:id/seats  
BS -> MS : GET /api/showtimes/:id (room_id)  
MS --> BS : Showtime details  
BS -> MS : GET /api/rooms/:room_id (rows, seats_per_row)  
MS --> BS : Room layout  
BS --> GW : Seat map (seat_number, status, type, surcharge)  
GW --> FE : Seat map  
FE --> C : Show seat grid\n(STANDARD / VIP +20k / COUPLE +50k)  
  
C -> FE : Click seats to select/deselect  
FE --> C : Update sidebar: selected seats,\nrunning total (base_price + surcharge)  
  
== Step 4: Confirm Booking ==  
  
C -> FE : Click "Book Now"  
FE -> GW : POST /api/bookings\n{showtime_id, seat_numbers: [...]}  
GW -> US : GET /api/auth/verify?token=...  
US --> GW : {valid: true, email, role}  
GW -> BS : POST /api/bookings\n+ X-User-Email header  
BS -> BS : Check seat availability for ALL seats  
BS -> MS : GET /api/showtimes/:id (base price)  
MS --> BS : Showtime price  
BS -> MS : GET /api/movies/:movie_id (title)  
MS --> BS : Movie title  
BS -> BS : Calculate total = SUM(base_price + surcharge)\nCreate booking record\nReserve all seats atomically  
BS -> MQ : Publish OrderPlacedEvent\n(queue: ticket_events)  
BS --> GW : {booking_id, total_price, movie, seats}  
GW --> FE : Booking response  
FE --> C : Redirect to /payment?booking_id=X&amount=Y  
  
== Step 5: Payment ==  
  
C -> FE : /payment page loads  
FE -> GW : GET /api/payment-methods  
GW -> PS : Forward (+ X-User-Email)  
PS --> GW : Saved cards list  
GW --> FE : Cards  
FE --> C : Show saved cards or\nprompt to add new card  
  
C -> FE : Click "Confirm Payment"  
FE -> GW : POST /api/payments {booking_id}  
GW -> US : Verify token  
US --> GW : Valid  
GW -> PS : POST /api/payments {booking_id}  
PS -> BS : GET /api/bookings/:id  
BS --> PS : {amount, customer_email}  
PS -> PS : Validate amount & email  
PS -> BS : PUT /api/bookings/:id/status\n{status: "confirmed"}  
BS --> PS : OK  
PS -> MQ : Publish INVOICE_PRINT\n(queue: invoice_events)  
PS --> GW : {message: "Payment successful",\namount_paid, status: "PAID"}  
GW --> FE : Payment success  
FE --> C : Alert "Payment successful!"\nRedirect to /my-bookings  
  
@enduml